name: First lines
description:
First lines is one of my first creation, created from custom javascript code, plotted on axidraw with red and blue ink.

Paper : 180g Canson paper
Format : A3 (297 x 420 mm)
Editions : 1/1
Date : 08/01/2021
Artist : Francis THOMAS (@fratodraw)

The NFT comes with the original drawing, international shipping included. Upon resale on the secondary market the original drawing shall be sent to the new owner. Shipping will be covered by the new owner.
